  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FastShoot is a true chess game in the world of first-person shooters:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy your enemies in the most unbelievable and spectacular ways - shoot, blow up, throw them over cliffs, throw them under deadly blows and use your abilities and surroundings wisely!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498960/extras/bd14e29ef385112643f2e97d62afb829.avif?t=1744657156\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncomplicated mechanics, familiar to every shooter fan!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498960/extras/2701c92c775abae84eb1001d5f84cde3.avif?t=1744657156\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of different opponents, requiring unique strategies and using special techniques for mass and spectacular destruction!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498960/extras/ed019d48decdc83160b4c1943532d57c.avif?t=1744657156\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique and interesting maps with parkour, shootouts or both elements at once!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498960/extras/16efb3605a7fab3eb36bb159dbd8308c.avif?t=1744657156\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p>",
